    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "809004006",
    "title": "公園での遊び方",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "桐生院トレーナーを誘い、日々の息抜きに\r\n公園に出かけると――",
            "enText": "She invites her trainer, Kiryuin, \nto go to the park to relax.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 66,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 8058854436150582774
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -5276190068939612422
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6463098509991677843,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "仕事に関係なく公園に来るのは、\r\n久しぶりな気がします。",
            "enText": "It's been a long time since I've been \nto the park, even for work.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -4774976164588675158
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 6004931768684499696
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2272225742292415666,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "……子どもの頃はよく、\r\n1人でも遊びに来ていたんですけど。",
            "enText": "… When I was a child, I used to \ncome here to play by myself.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "1人でも？",
                    "enText": "Even one?",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 5492179193081900413
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -7406644723616824236
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -9137247058969893450,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "と、友だちもいましたよ？\r\nでもあの……1人で遊ぶのも好きで。",
            "enText": "And I had friends, you know? But I also like \nto play with that…1 person.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 55,
                    "pathId": -2597451882296601101
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -4780474573340997109
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1097426821408524839,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "例えばジャングルジムの1番上で空を眺め、\r\n『月刊トゥインクル』を読んだり……。",
            "enText": "For example, at the top of the jungle \ngym, looking at the sky and reading \nTwinkle Monthly…",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 25,
                    "pathId": 5721619368399949283
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 25,
                    "pathId": 1892603968010134753
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5630880171309322828,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "ブランコに座りながら、\r\n『トレーナー白書』を読んだり……。",
            "enText": "Sitting on the swing, reading \nthe White Book of Trainers…",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "pathId": 7628554140729755839,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "色々、楽しんでいたんですよ。",
            "enText": "We were having a lot of fun.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 54,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "どっちも読書では",
                    "enText": "Both in reading",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": -6387472998830578661
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 2448329363110043086
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 103,
                    "pathId": -7832733942119417200
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2168252226975646220,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "あっ、いえ！　これはお気に入りの話で、\r\nちゃんと遊具を使った遊びもしてました！",
            "enText": "Oh, no! That's my favourite story, and I did \nget to play on the playground equipment!",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 7952748575086280678
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": -9040157880009185910
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -4197942525122972053
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4306791544912617711,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "シーソーとか、鉄棒とかでっ。",
            "enText": "On the seesaw and the iron bar.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 54,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "1人でシーソーですか……？",
                    "enText": "A seesaw all by yourself?…?",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "鉄棒、得意な技があったり？",
                    "enText": "Do you have a special skill on the bars?",
                    "nextBlock": 22
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 48,
                    "pathId": -7348464356935854296
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 5181077760629138878
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 520088991855557223,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "はいっ。大人の立場としては、\r\n子どもたちに教えることはできませんが……。",
            "enText": "Yes. As an adult, I can't tell you what to \ndo with your children…",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 57,
                    "pathId": 2935550912975518428
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -8300453105484635740
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6271672715972797164,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "シーソーの端から端へ、歩いて渡るんです。\r\nこれが意外とバランス感覚が鍛えられて！",
            "enText": "You have to walk across the seesaw \nfrom one end to the other. It's \na great balance exercise!",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -6621120455609933372
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -5248104762537830024
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7776778017375365796,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "コツは反対側に渡った時に少しだけ\r\n体勢を低くすることですが――",
            "enText": "The trick is to stay a little lower when you \ncross to the other side.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 63,
                    "pathId": -4443017345577480685
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 3414717098727124931
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8600990875133513563,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "感覚を強化したいのであれば、\r\n常に正しい姿勢を取り続けた方がいいですね。",
            "enText": "If you want to strengthen your senses, you \nshould always keep a correct posture.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -7440595728094452424
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": 3019832117930174174
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -2404655052312696290
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3737657646175588619,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "そうですっ、やってみせましょうか！\r\n見ててくださいねっ。",
            "enText": "Yes, I'll do it! You'll have to watch.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 58,
                    "pathId": -973377358606158473
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 58,
                    "pathId": 5403766487370526265
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6233649931811112675,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "よっ。座るところは避けて……\r\n背筋を伸ばしたら、真っ直ぐに……。",
            "enText": "Yo. Avoid the place where you sit … \nstraighten your back and then straighten…",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 66,
            "pathId": 6329885801034391231,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "ほらほら、ここですっ。\r\nここでガクンッとなるんですけど――",
            "enText": "Here, here, here. Here's where it clicks…",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "pathId": -8064439228192028323,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "桐生院は両手でバランスをとりながら、\r\nシーソーを渡り切った。\n……とてもとても自慢げに。",
            "enText": "Kiryuin balanced on her hands and crossed \nthe seesaw… very, very proudly.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 74,
            "pathId": -5386088147647303157,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "いかがでした？　私、バランス感覚には\r\n自信があって、お友だちにも褒められ……。",
            "enText": "How did you like it? I'm very confident in \nmy balance and my friends praise me for it…",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": -458084108940454777
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": -2314193000058918983
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 2411171831160309184
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 641333028704570456,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "……あ。す、すみません、ベラベラと。",
            "enText": "… Oh. I'm sorry, I'm blabbing.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 56,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "自分もやってみます！",
                    "enText": "I'll try it myself!",
                    "nextBlock": 20
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": -4861522906356759622
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 8714726685521281448
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 3926505418551968196
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 818853266574520955,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "！　ええ、是非！　隣でフォローしますから、\r\n安心してくださいねっ。",
            "enText": "Yes! Yes, please! I'll be right \nnext to you, so don't worry.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": 4016932276187931588
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 4107213827179047829
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7039088071302691263,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "子どもがいないことを確認しつつ、\r\n桐生院トレーナーとシーソーで遊んだ。",
            "enText": "I played seesaw with trainer Kiryuin, \nmaking sure that there were no children.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 2159887626993509741
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 9043122420606659514
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6690993664324242682,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "はいっ、懸垂です！！",
            "enText": "Yes, pull-ups!",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 51,
            "trainerGender": "f",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -2728004023986529181
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 4243705917629826554
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8957836350140809092,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "いきなり無理はせず、自分の力に合わせて\r\n少しずつ慣らしていくのがコツです。",
            "enText": "The trick is not to push yourself too hard, \nbut to get used to it gradually and \naccording to your own strength.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "trainerGender": "f",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -4020985014935234866
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 2553537688398323159
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7024186139438097085,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "最初は10回……5回でもいいんです。",
            "enText": "You can start with 10…5 times.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 56,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -3908158798979483516
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 8540083254970455128
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 8948164015580787657
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7948323478633481637,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "大切なのは結果です。これは過程を\r\n無視するということではありません。",
            "enText": "It is the result that counts. This does not \nmean that we ignore the process.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": 7135943156418355335
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 2817731308957533345
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -69307130401896658,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "正しい過程があるからこそ、\r\n結果に辿り着けるという――",
            "enText": "The right process is the only way \nto get to the right result.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "それは遊びではなくトレーニングでは？",
                    "enText": "Isn't that training, not play?",
                    "nextBlock": 27
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 48,
                    "pathId": 4847935530410044997
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 5506500294627530329
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2175312028688843806,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "………………はっ！！！！！",
            "enText": "… is ！！！！！",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 53,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 7051443181274651161
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 866781480017853380
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5460878741607583819,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "だ、だとすると、私……\r\n公園で遊んだことないのでは……？",
            "enText": "Well, if that's the case, I've… never played \nin a park before, have I…?",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 46,
                    "pathId": -1304013882840258959
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 1214910448200159256
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3654853279469916594,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "衝撃の事実に気付いた顔の\r\n桐生院トレーナーを誘い、\n一緒にブランコで遊ぶことにした。",
            "enText": "With a shocked look on her face, she invites \nKiryuin to play on the swings with her.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 85,
                    "pathId": -8233638102301550416
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -4356018045076471278
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6155508052231914427,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "最初はあまりできなかったんですが、\r\n徐々に慣れてきて、結果100回ほど！",
            "enText": "At first I couldn't do it very well, but \nthen I got used to it and ended up doing it \nabout a hundred times!",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "trainerGender": "f",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": 8840009792777149073
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -2574254743662336616
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2017750185843492570,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "桐生院トレーナー",
            "enName": "Kiryuin Aoi",
            "jpText": "……そういえば、最近はやっていませんね。\r\n試してみてもいいですか？",
            "enText": "… By the way, I haven't done this \nrecently. Can I give it a try?",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 26,
                    "pathId": 6942401430282439469
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -4692726481727879567
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 6000239292249424842
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7082151132206870281,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "気合いを入れ、真剣な顔で懸垂する\r\n桐生院トレーナーを応援した。",
            "enText": "I cheered on my trainer, Kiryuin, who looked \nvery serious as she did her pull-ups.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 66,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -786758685007007457
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -4918624227507969874
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -6416332509970218108
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3527884133499088488,
            "blockIdx": 32
        }
    ],
